SR; LIBERALS; TELEVISION PROGRAMMING; MOTION PICTURES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA011489-0061 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 5301 </DOCID>
