complete a comeback for Fullerton, which trailed by as many as 16 in the fourth 
quarter at La Habra. Guard Rene Arias helped the Fullerton comeback with 32 
points. He had 8 3-pointers, including 4 in the fourth quarter. Fullerton is 
10-5, 3-0. 
</P>
